headline: AvalonBay Communities’ (AVB) Q2 Results Beat Estimates amid Construction Spree
summary: AvalonBay Communities, Inc. (NYSE:AVB) is one of the best depressed stocks to buy in 2025. On July 30, the company delivered solid second-quarter results. Earnings per share were up 5.6% year-over-year to $1.88, better than the analyst estimate of $1.20 a share. Same-store residential revenue was up 3% year-over-year to $689.1 million in the quarter […]
